      "section": [
        "Royal Procession"
      ],
      "text": "The Royal Procession, also known as the Imperial Firebenders, was a unit of elite firebenders who served as personal and ceremonial guards for the Fire Nation Royal Family, and also worked in close association with the Fire Lord's military maneuvers."
    },
    {
      "body": "During the six hundred-day ${link_0} of ${link_1}, two Imperial Firebenders stood at ${link_2}'s side while he wrote a letter home to ${link_3} and ${link_4}.",
      "links": [
        {
          "body": "Siege",
          "key": "${link_0}",
