            "href": "/wiki/Ty_Lee",
            "page": "Ty_Lee"
          }
        }
      ],
      "section": [
        "Royal Procession",
        "History"
      ],
      "text": "Five years later, while Azula was attempting to capture her brother and uncle, she was accompanied by at least thirty\u00a0of these soldiers on her ship. Iroh and Zuko were able to defeat these soldiers easily after discovering that the former two were about to be taken prisoner. When advised by Lo and Li, Azula decided to leave the Royal Procession in favor of a smaller, elite team, and set off to enlist Mai and Ty Lee."
    },
    {
      "body": "During the ${link_0}, they were seen in Fire Lord ${link_1}'s secret bunker, serving as protection during the eclipse in the event that an enemy managed to breach the underground facility. As they were deprived of their bending, they were carrying polearms.",
      "links": [
        {
          "body": "Day of Black Sun",
          "key": "${link_0}",
          "target": {
            "external": false,
            "href": "/wiki/Day_of_Black_Sun",
