          }
        },
        {
          "body": "Ozai",
          "key": "${link_1}",
          "target": {
            "external": false,
            "href": "/wiki/Ozai",
            "page": "Ozai"
          }
        }
      ],
      "section": [
        "Royal Procession",
        "History"
      ],
      "text": "During the Day of Black Sun, they were seen in Fire Lord Ozai's secret bunker, serving as protection during the eclipse in the event that an enemy managed to breach the underground facility. As they were deprived of their bending, they were carrying polearms."
    },
    {
      "body": "The Royal Procession took a small role in the coronation of ${link_0} Ozai, holding up the banners of the Phoenix King.",
      "links": [
        {
          "body": "Phoenix King",
          "key": "${link_0}",
          "target": {
            "external": false,
            "href": "/wiki/Phoenix_King",
            "page": "Phoenix_King"
          }
        }
      ],
      "section": [
        "Royal Procession",
        "History"
      ],
      "text": "The Royal Procession took a small role in the coronation of Phoenix King Ozai, holding up the banners of the Phoenix King."
    },
    {
      "body": "Before her coronation as Fire Lord, Azula slipped into a case of severe paranoia and ended up banishing nearly all her staff, including the Imperial Firebenders present at the palace, as mentioned by Lo and Li. Imperial Firebenders were seen as part of the crew of the ${link_0} ${link_1}, burning a large section of ${link_2} and defending the ships from intruders.",
      "links": [
        {
          "body": "airship",
          "key": "${link_0}",
          "target": {
            "external": false,
            "href": "/wiki/Fire_Nation_airship",
            "page": "Fire_Nation_airship"
          }
        },
        {
          "body": "fleet",
          "key": "${link_1}",
          "target": {
